---
import Layout from "../../components/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Martinkvito">
  <section class="project-section">
    <h1>Martinkvito</h1>
    <img src="/project_photos/martinkvito.png" alt="screenshot of website" class="large-project-image" />
    <div class="project-description">
    
    <p>Available on <a href="https://kvito.martinstyve.no/" target="_blank">kvito.martinstyve.no</a>. Source code can be found on my <a href="https://github.com/martinstyve/martinkvito" target="_blank">Github</a></p>
      
    <p>Made as a pitch for friends at <a href="https://www.studentbergen.no/studentorganisasjoner/inkogvito-linjeforening-for-kognitiv-vitenskap-ved-uib/" target="_blank">Inkogvito</a>. to get their own website and webkom.
        Tech stack is primarily Next.js and Sanity, inspired by <a href="https://github.com/Project-insert-name/root-website" target="_blank">Root linjeforening</a>. Site is self hosted.</p>

    <p>Project is split in two parts. A static blog page which can be viewed by visiting the site, and a "studio" site, <a href="https://martinkvito.sanity.studio" target="_blank">martinkvito.sanity.studio</a> where anyone (with access) can create and modify blog posts without ever touching the code base.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
<style>
  .project-section {
    padding: 4rem 1rem;
    background-color: #1e1e24;
    color: #f1f1f1;
    text-align: center;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #5DD5FF;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #c4c4c4;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  a {
  color: #1e90ff; /* Standard blue color */
  text-decoration: underline;
}

a:hover {
  color: #63b3ff; /* Lighter blue on hover */
  text-decoration: underline;
}

  .large-project-image {
    width: 100%; 
    height: auto;
    max-width: 400px;
    border-radius: 8px; 
    margin-bottom: 2rem; 
  }

  .project-description {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .project-links {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem; /* Space between the logos */
  }

  .logo-link {
    width: 80px; /* Adjust the logo size */
    height: auto;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .logo-link:hover {
    filter: opacity(0.8) drop-shadow(0 0 10px #5DD5FF);
    transform: scale(1.1); /* Scale up the logo on hover */
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .large-project-image {
      max-width: 100%; /* Allow the image to be responsive */
    }

    .project-section {
      padding: 2rem 1rem; /* Adjust padding for smaller screens */
    }
  }
</style>
